                Risus ultricies tristique nulla aliquet enim
                tortor.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <p local-class="heading-3">Chorus</p>
              <p local-class="lyrics">
                Aliquet eget sit amet tellus cras adipiscing. ♫
              </p>
              <p local-class="lyrics">
